JOHANNESBURG - Writer, journalist, actor and film critic Leon van Nierop speaks about his latest steamy offering, Toyboy. It tells the story of a 26-year-old escort to Johannesburg’s rich and powerful women. The book launch takes place on Wednesday at Book Revue in Birdhaven, Johannesburg. * eNCA's Andrea Van Wyk sat down with an author who's written over 20 books. Watch the video in the gallery above. eNCA